==================
=  Description:  =
==================

An implementation of a hangman game using some images and a python programme.
we also have a hint function to assist the user, and in the end of each game the user has the option of playing again
The programme asks the user for input in each iteration in order to determine the next display.

=============================
=  List of submitted files: =
=============================

README - this file
ex4.py - contains all the function and documentation regarding the functions implementation.
The user interface and rules of the hangman game are a given knowledge of the user.
we imported few images and a gui file in order to make the UI/UX smooth (all given in the exercise) 



